{"title":"夸食堂","authors":[],"dates":[{"year":1958,"month":11,"day":13}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"夸食堂"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"杏花村，桃花庄，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"八个老婆夸食堂；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"桂花茶，丰收汤，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"八宝米饭喷喷香。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老人吃了食堂饭，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"寿比南山万年长；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"青年吃了食堂饭，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挑起泰山赶太阳；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"妇女吃了食堂饭，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"个个变成巧姑娘；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小孩吃了食堂饭，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一夜长成托天王；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"铁匠吃了食堂饭，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三间草棚能炼钢；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"木匠吃了食堂饭，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"能叫石磨长翅膀；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"干部吃了食堂饭，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心中升起红太阳；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"社员都吃食堂饭，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"石坡也能产米粮。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":3,"page_end":3}